decks.notes: The deck is centered around using Heliod, Sun-Crowned as the commander to create a powerful combo strategy. The deck features a mix of creatures and enchantments that support the combo potential of Heliod, such as Auriok Champion and Bishop of Wings to gain life and create tokens, as well as cards like Walking Ballista and Spike Feeder to take advantage of Heliod's ability to put +1/+1 counters on creatures. The deck also includes a variety of protection spells and removal to control the board and protect the combo pieces. Overall, the deck aims to assemble the combo pieces efficiently while maintaining a strong board presence to outpace and outvalue the opponent in a 1 vs 1 Duel Commander format.
